EN: The conclusions in this report contradict the previous research findings.

ZH: 她的态度对于同一个问题好像总是自相矛盾。
EN: Her attitude towards the same issue always seems contradictory.

ZH: 我们不能接受一个自相矛盾的解释。
EN: We cannot accept a contradictory explanation.

