EN: The viewpoints in this book contradict the previous chapters.

ZH: 他的行为和他之前的承诺自相矛盾。
EN: His actions contradict his previous promises.

ZH: 她一会儿说喜欢这个设计，一会儿又说不喜欢，真是自相矛盾。
EN: She says she likes this design one moment and dislikes it the next, truly contradictory.

ZH: 这两个目击者关于事件的描述自相矛盾。
EN: The descriptions of the event by these two eyewitnesses are contradictory.

